values:
Kehlencrow, I think I finally got it figured out. I'll just break up my chapters and do all the technical crap I need to do before uploading it. I hate doing HTML.

To those who have come here:

I had written two fics(almost finished the second one) where the HP books are commented on(or parodied) by characters from the books.

Someone complained about my fics and they were taken down. I will now be posting them here.

First Fic:

Slytherins And Gryffindors Read Harry Potter And The Sorcerers Stone

Summary: A book from the future is sent back into the past. Three Weasleys, The Headmaster, Two Professors and A Malfoy are stuck in the Staff Room and must read this book. Enjoy!
